<p>Thanks for presentation copy of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p>  
<p>Mivart’s <hi rend="italic">Genesis of species</hi> [1871] is poor.</p> 
            <p>Mathematical illustrations of Pangenesis at Cambridge.</p> 
